<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 1in;
        }
        
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
            font-family: 'Arial', 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #dc2626;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .document-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b91c1c;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .section-header {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b91c1c;
            margin: 30px 0 15px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }
        
        .subsection-header {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #374151;
            margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .content-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        
        .bullet-point {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .bullet-point::before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: -15px;
            color: #dc2626;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .metrics-box {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .metrics-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b91c1c;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .metric-item {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-left: 15px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .metric-item::before {
            content: "▶";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .company-logo {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b91c1c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="document-title">{{title}}</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Strategic Growth Plan 2024-2025</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section-header">Executive Summary</div>
    <div class="content-text">MM Docs is positioned to become the leading AI-powered document generation platform for businesses worldwide. Our strategic focus centers on delivering exceptional value through intelligent automation, professional quality, and seamless user experience.</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Market Opportunity</div>
    <div class="content-text">The global document automation market is valued at $500M+ and growing at 15% annually. Key drivers include:</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Increasing demand for digital transformation in document workflows</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Rising costs of manual document creation and management</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Growing need for brand consistency across business communications</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Expansion of remote work requiring standardized documentation</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Target Market Segments</div>
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Primary Markets:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Small to Medium Businesses (SMBs) seeking professional document automation</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Freelancers and consultants requiring branded business documents</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">HR departments managing employee documentation at scale</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Sales teams generating proposals, quotations, and contracts</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Secondary Markets:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Legal firms requiring standardized document templates</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Accounting firms creating client-facing financial documents</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Marketing agencies managing multiple client brands</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Competitive Advantages</div>
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Technology Leadership:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Advanced AI integration with OpenRouter for superior content generation</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Comprehensive template library covering 25+ document categories</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Intelligent brand kit integration for consistent visual identity</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Real-time document preview and editing capabilities</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>User Experience Excellence:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Intuitive category-based document selection</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Detailed form inputs for precise document customization</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Instant PDF and DOCX export functionality</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Mobile-responsive design for accessibility</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Growth Initiatives</div>
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Phase 1 (Q1-Q2 2024): Foundation & Optimization</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Enhance AI content quality and accuracy</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Expand template library to 50+ document types</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Implement user feedback system for continuous improvement</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Optimize conversion funnel from free to premium users</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Phase 2 (Q3-Q4 2024): Scale & Expansion</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Launch enterprise features with team collaboration</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Introduce API access for third-party integrations</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Develop industry-specific template collections</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Implement advanced analytics and reporting</div>
    
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Phase 3 (2025): Market Leadership</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Multi-language support for global expansion</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">White-label solutions for agencies and consultants</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Advanced AI features including document analysis</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Strategic partnerships with business software providers</div>
    
    <div class="subsection-header">Revenue Strategy</div>
    <div class="content-text"><strong>Freemium Model:</strong></div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Free tier: 5 documents per month with MM Docs branding</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Pro tier: ₹999/month for unlimited documents, brand customization</div>
    <div class="bullet-point">Enterprise tier: Custom pricing for teams and advanced features</div>
    
    <div class="metrics-box">
        <div class="metrics-title">Key Success Metrics</div>
        <div class="metric-item">Target: 10,000 active users by Q4 2024</div>
        <div class="metric-item">Conversion rate goal: 15% free to premium</div>
        <div class="metric-item">Monthly recurring revenue target: ₹1.5M by end of 2024</div>
        <div class="metric-item">Customer acquisition cost: <₹500 per premium user</div>
        <div class="metric-item">User retention: 80% monthly retention rate</div>
        <div class="metric-item">Document generation: 100,000+ documents created monthly</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="company-logo">MM Docs</div>
        <div>Strategic Growth & Business Excellence</div>
        <div>AI-Powered Document Solutions</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>